29
00:01:15,110 --> 00:01:16,780
♪Or just let it go?♪

30
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:20,920
I'm back.

31
00:01:21,750 --> 00:01:25,380
♪I stay under the limp spring blossom♪

32
00:01:25,460 --> 00:01:28,890
♪Trimming off all the mess♪

33
00:01:29,270 --> 00:01:35,590
♪So happiness may bloom flawlessly♪

34
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:39,840
Gu Cheng and I

35
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,960
confirmed that Mom is clear.

36
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:43,840
But we speculate

37
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:45,240
that she might possess

38
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:46,880
the evidence of the mastermind.

39
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,440
So,

40
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,880
we will continue pretending
we don't get along

41
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:53,000
to ensure your safety.

42
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:55,240
All right.

43
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,360
Don't laugh.

44
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:07,280
I haven't forgiven you yet.

45
00:03:09,180 --> 00:03:11,210
[Eat lunch first. I'll be right back.]

46
00:03:11,410 --> 00:03:14,520
[Love you forever]

47
00:03:15,330 --> 00:03:17,320
♪It sails through the mist♪

48
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:22,160
♪Stained with dust
that can't be shaken off♪

49
00:03:22,730 --> 00:03:26,190
♪Waiting for a cloud to return♪

50
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:28,500
♪Raindrops fall♪

51
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:33,580
♪Washing away the gloom underneath♪

52
00:03:33,990 --> 00:03:38,010
♪I saw you retreat in darkness♪

53
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:38,960
I'm back.

54
00:03:39,780 --> 00:03:44,310
♪I heard a pounding heart
swoon with love♪

55
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:50,720
You were dozing off this morning.

56
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,800
Eat something.

57
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,720
All right?

58
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:59,120
You must live a long life.

59
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:02,360
I have already lost one of my brothers.

60
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,600
I know

61
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,080
Zejia had always been generous to you,

62
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,160
and you both had

63
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,360
a really deep bond.

64
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:12,520
But, Xin,

65
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,240
we can't avoid separation.

66
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,880
The thing is that Zejia was so young

67
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:18,000
and intelligent.

68
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:19,920
I thought he would've survived.

69
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:24,520
Eat something first.

70
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:25,400
All right?

71
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,600
Do you think

72
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:30,280
burning books in my own yard

73
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,080
is considered arson?

74
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:36,040
Sign charts and Bagua are just nonsense.

75
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:38,320
Fortune telling and metaphysics
aren't real.

76
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,000
Cheng.

77
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,480
I'm going to burn those books.

78
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,560
All right.

79
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,160
Burn them if you like.

80
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:44,680
Eat the congee.

81
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:47,000
I cooked it just now.

82
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:50,960
Cheng.

83
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:53,160
You're the best.

84
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:56,320
Ze'an is really disappointing.

85
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,040
This won't do.

86
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:02,480
I have you with me.

87
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:04,320
But Zhen is alone now.

88
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,440
She is more upset.

89
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,400
Cheng.

90
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:09,000
Pack the breakfast.

91
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:09,920
I'm sending over this to her.

92
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,360
I'll go get ready

93
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,560
and set off soon.

94
00:05:16,050 --> 00:05:16,860
[Ma Jun]

95
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:24,040
I'm a little short on cash.

96
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:24,840
I need your help.

97
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,080
Stop calling me.

98
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,520
I'm afraid you won't want
to eat other food.

99
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:34,560
Cheng cooked this himself.

100
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,760
Does it smell good?

101
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:36,520
Try it.

102
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,680
You didn't sleep well, did you?

103
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:41,880
Zejia...

104
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,640
Well, I'm saying

105
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:45,760
that you should get over this.

106
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:46,800
Forget the past

107
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,880
and embrace tomorrow.

108
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,080
Start

109
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,520
a brand new relationship.

110
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:54,160
I know you and Zejia
had a really deep bond.

111
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:56,640
But you can't dwell on low energy.

112
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,720
It's bad.

113
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,920
Use it as a method to heal yourself.
Go ahead and try.

114
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,240
Sure.

115
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,400
(Dew on the petals.)

116
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,000
(The flowers are freshly bought.)

117
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:20,480
(Zhen is a lucky woman.)

118
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,920
(Am I worrying for nothing?)

119
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,840
(But she just moved on too fast.)

120
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,280
The congee is yummy.
I'll go and get ready.

121
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,200
Where are you going?

122
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,720
I'm visiting Mom tonight.

123
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,840
I was so upset yesterday,
and I forgot about her.

124
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,680
You're so thoughtful, Zhen.

125
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,600
Back then,

126
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,400
Mom always said that I was impatient.

127
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,400
She wanted me to practice calligraphy

128
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,480
and learn how to brew tea

129
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,160
to become composed.

130
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,200
Over these years,

131
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:02,080
it's the first time
you've mentioned your family.

132
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,480
I've never told you

133
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:06,920
that my mom

134
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:09,240
is the technical director
of Anshi Group,

135
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:11,840
who was fired
due to the corruption case.

136
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,400
Are you...

137
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,200
I'm Wu Wenzhao's daughter.

138
00:07:27,370 --> 00:07:30,980
♪Waiting for the wilted flower
to finally fall silent♪

139
00:07:31,420 --> 00:07:34,860
♪Waiting for the time
to divide the sunset glow♪

140
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:38,590
♪He stalks my mind and memories♪

141
00:07:39,070 --> 00:07:42,500
♪Struggling in this perpetual cycle♪

142
00:07:42,890 --> 00:07:46,540
♪Promises are answering his lies♪

143
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:50,190
♪I'm just a walker-on
in this tear-jerker♪

144
00:07:50,410 --> 00:07:54,030
♪Tick, tock, tick, tock♪

145
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:57,060
♪Tears are speaking♪

146
